column5: Deer Fight Interrupted by a Single Bullet    This is not what you would expect.  Watch it, even if you don't like hunting.  Two deer are locked up in a fight and would have died a slow death.  See what a hunter does with a bullet.  It has a good ending. Have the volume turned up.  http://www.texashuntfish.com/app/forum/25824/Deer-Fight-Interrupted-by-a
